OL,7,FA Borders ice rink marking its 60th
OL,8,Fanniversary looks ahead to a weekend
OL,9,Fof celebration after overcoming a
OL,10,F'difficult few years'.
OL,12,FThis time last year Borders Ice Rink
OL,13,Fwas fighting for survival following
OL,14,Ftheir struggles in keeping up with the
OL,15,Fcost of energy bills.
OL,17,FThe ice rink has now turned a corner
OL,18,Fand will be celebrating its 60th
OL,19,Fbirthday with a curling competition
OL,20,Fthis weekend.
