OL,7,FThe ice rink, in Kelso, opened its
OL,8,Fdoors to the public in 1964.
OL,10,FLucy Tile, the Chair of Border Ice
OL,11,FRink, says the facility had to adapt
OL,12,Fto bringing more people after
OL,13,Fsurviving the pandemic and energy
OL,14,Fcrisis.
OL,16,FShe said: "It has been very tricky
OL,17,Fover the last few years, we've had to
OL,18,Fhunker down and look at all options to
OL,19,Fcarry on."
